dct_title_s: Le nouveau plan de Grenoble : avec les nouvelles rues
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Map shows commune boundary, railways, roads in construction, and cable car lines. With an index of roads and places of interest. Map on verso: Excursions autour de Grenoble. Text, altitude list, and advertisements on verso.
